      static Future<void> configureMedia({bool isForced = false}) async {
    92

      static Future<void> configureRecorder({

      static Future<void> _selectBluetoothInputIfAvailable() async {
    119
        if (Platform.isAndroid) return;
    120
    121
        try {
    122
          final avSession = AVAudioSession();
    123
    124
          final currentInput = await avSession.currentRoute.then((route) => route.inputs.firstOrNull);
    125
          final isCurrentInputBluetooth =
    126
              currentInput?.portType == AVAudioSessionPort.bluetoothHfp ||
    127
              currentInput?.portType == AVAudioSessionPort.bluetoothA2dp ||
    128
              currentInput?.portType == AVAudioSessionPort.bluetoothLe;
    129
    130
          loggy.info(
    131
            '[AudioSession] Current input: ${currentInput?.portName} (${currentInput?.portType.name}), isBluetooth: $isCurrentInputBluetooth',
    132
          );
    133
    134
          if (isCurrentInputBluetooth) {
    135
            loggy.info('[AudioSession] Bluetooth input already selected, skipping');
    136
            return;
    137
          }
    138
    139
          final availableInputs = await avSession.availableInputs;
    140
    141
          loggy.info(
    142
            '[AudioSession] Available inputs: ${availableInputs.map((i) => '${i.portName} (${i.portType.name})').join(', ')}',
    143
          );
    144
    145
          final bluetoothInput = availableInputs.cast<AVAudioSessionPortDescription?>().firstWhere(
    146
            (input) =>
    147
                input?.portType == AVAudioSessionPort.bluetoothHfp ||
    148
                input?.portType == AVAudioSessionPort.bluetoothA2dp ||
    149
                input?.portType == AVAudioSessionPort.bluetoothLe,
    150
            orElse: () => null,
    151
          );
    152
    153
          if (bluetoothInput != null) {
    154
            loggy.info(
    155
              '[AudioSession] Selecting Bluetooth input: ${bluetoothInput.portName} (${bluetoothInput.portType.name})',
    156
            );
    157
    158
            final session = await AudioSession.instance;
    159
            await session.setActive(false);
    160
            await avSession.setPreferredInput(bluetoothInput);
    161
            await session.setActive(true);
    162
    163
            loggy.info('[AudioSession] Bluetooth input selected and session reactivated');
    164
          } else {
    165
            loggy.info('[AudioSession] No Bluetooth input available');
    166
          }
    167
        } catch (e, sT) {
    168
          loggy.warning(
    169
            '[AudioSession] Failed to select Bluetooth input',
    170
            exception: e,
    171
            stacktrace: sT,
    172
          );
    173
        }
    174
      }

      Future<void> configure({required bool isForced}) async {
    177
        try {
    178
          final session = await AudioSession.instance;
    179
          final sessionConfiguration = session.configuration;
    180
          final currentSettings = sessionConfiguration != null
    181
              ? AudioSettings._fromConfiguration(sessionConfiguration)
    182
              : null;
    183
    184
          final isAlreadyConfigured = currentSettings == this;
    185
    186
          loggy.info(
    187
            '[AudioSession] Forced: $isForced, configured: $isAlreadyConfigured, config: $isForced ${toJson()}',
    188
          );
    189
    190
          if (!isForced && isAlreadyConfigured) {
    191
            return;
    192
          }
    193
    194
          await session.configure(_toConfiguration());
    195
          await _activateSession(session);
    196
          await _enableHapticForIOS();
    197
          loggy.info('[AudioSession] Finished configuration');
    198
        } catch (e, sT) {
    199
          loggy.error('[AudioSession] Failed configuration', exception: e, stacktrace: sT);
    200
        }
    201
      }
